-- USAA Will Add 3,500 Jobs as Membership Rolls Projected to Expand
-- B y   E l i z a b e t h   B u n n
-- 2013-03-05T19:19:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-05/usaa-will-add-3-500-jobs-as-membership-rolls-projected-to-expand.html
United States Automobile
Association, the provider of insurance and other financial
services to military personnel, said it will add as many as
3,500 net new jobs over the next three years.  The positions include member contact representatives in
investments, insurance, banking and claims, the San Antonio-
based company said today in a statement distributed by  Business
Wire . The initial expansions will be in San Antonio and Phoenix,
and may result in as many as 1,000 news jobs in San Antonio by
the end of 2015, according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elizabeth Bunn in  New York  at 
 ebunn1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
